# Convivo Design System Rules

## Design System Structure

### 1. Token Definitions

**Location**: `src/assets/scss/_variables.scss`
**Format**: SCSS variables with CSS custom properties integration

**Color System**:
```scss
// Primary colors using Material Design tokens
$primary: var(--mat-sys-primary);
$secondary: var(--mat-sys-secondary);
$accent: var(--mat-sys-secondary);
$error: var(--mat-sys-error);
$warning: #f8c20a;
$success: #36c76c;
$white: #ffffff;

// Light variants
$light-primary: var(--mat-sys-primary-fixed-dim);
$light-secondary: var(--mat-sys-secondary-fixed-dim);
$light-error: var(--mat-sys-error-fixed-dim);
$light-warning: #f8c20a26;
$light-success: #36c76c26;
```

**Typography**:
```scss
$font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
$text-color: var(--mat-sys-on-background);
```

**Layout & Spacing**:
```scss
$sidenav-desktop: 265px;
$sidenav-mini: 80px;
$header-height: 70px;
$border-radius: 12px;
$card-spacer: 30px;
$boxedWidth: 1200px;
```

### 2. Component Library

**Architecture**: Angular standalone components with SCSS modules
**Location**: `src/app/components/` and `src/app/pages/`

**Component Structure**:
```
component-name/
├── component-name.component.html
├── component-name.component.ts
├── component-name.component.scss (optional)
└── component-name.component.spec.ts
```

**Example Component**:
```typescript
import { Component } from '@angular/core';
import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-blog-card',
  standalone: true,
  imports: [CommonModule],
  templateUrl: './blog-card.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./blog-card.component.scss']
})
export class BlogCardComponent {
  // Component logic
}
```

